{"Sid":0,"Did":126916,"Id":"604555","Title":"冬山定安宮正殿室內側牆彩繪","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collection/57b4d705-c61d-4511-b1db-b8590797c4b0/109-her-pa-2503-202011141601465faf66a9552b80.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collection/8a6d5e31-aae7-457b-a79e-f5b5cc48bea7/109-her-pa-2503-202011141601465faf66a9552b81.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n　　冬山定安宮為單殿式廟宇，除步口廊對看牆有水泥模塑之「蒼龍教子」、「母虎相送」的龍虎主題外，在正殿室內兩側牆面亦以大面積彩繪方式，彩繪同為龍虎主題的「降龍羅漢」與「伏虎羅漢」，二者都是由清乾隆皇帝所頒定之羅漢。\n\n　　龍邊壁面之「降龍羅漢」彩繪，可見上為層雲，下為翻湧海浪，惡龍身體由內往外，龍首與降龍羅漢相對，右前爪伸向降龍羅漢。降龍羅漢為釋迦牟尼得道弟子十八羅漢之一的迦葉尊者，臺灣民間咸信濟公禪師即降龍羅漢轉世。\n\n　　虎邊壁面之「伏虎羅漢」彩繪，可見上為樹林，下為崎嶇山岩，伏虎羅漢立於山岩之上，猛虎踞於山岩下方，頭朝伏虎羅漢。伏虎羅漢為釋迦牟尼得道弟子十八羅漢之一的彌勒尊者。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.789241","Keyword_Latitude":"24.634958","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/B86622C6-FB6C-4903-9D64-6E30CDD9212C","Original_Identifier":"604555","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"伏虎羅漢 / 迦葉尊者 / 降龍羅漢 / 彌勒尊者","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2021/01/06 18:48:38","timelines":"","place":"","address":"宜蘭縣冬山鄉冬山路305號","longitude":"121.789241","latitude":"24.634958","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"無","writer":"蔡明志/ 林立晨","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collectionOpen/4f9a2132-1177-402d-a65e-05d386679a64/109-her-pa-2503-re-202011141604065faf66a9552b80.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collectionOpen/f97a2ea2-fde2-496d-a846-8b368b8e5798/109-her-pa-2503-re-202011141604065faf6